# Trivy ignore file
# Format: CVE-YYYY-XXXXX  expiry_date  reason
# Format: GHSA-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx  expiry_date  reason
# Leave expiry_date blank to ignore indefinitely
#
# Examples (uncomment and customize as needed):
# CVE-2021-44228  2024-12-31  log4shell - not affected (no log4j in project)
# GHSA-jfh8-c2jp-jggg  no-fix  upstream dependency, no fix available yet
